data.name: mafia-madness
data.description: A dynamic online version of the classic party game Mafia, built with Java and React, featuring a PostgreSQL database for real-time game state management. This project focuses on full-stack development, interactive UI design, and scalable back-end architecture.

data.name: Music-EraVision
data.description: A deep learning-powered tool for classifying sheet music into Baroque, Classical, and Romantic style periods. Built using ResNet152. A custom data pipeline automates metadata removal and format conversion, utilizing Playwright. The tech stack includes Python, PyTorch, and Playwright.
